{"tid":2249027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍頻頻發布造假影片 引發中國網友質疑","createTime":"2020-10-19T05:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:18:31.000Z","uid":337052,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9be6f9ec50540421be961985fbb82591548e7100","tid":2249027,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">又造假？解放軍發布誓師影片 指揮台橫幅打馬賽克挨批「見不得人」</span></strong><br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 楊清緣 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2020.10.19 | 05:54<br />\n     <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/482/5f8cb6becb5d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F482%2F5f8cb6becb5d5.jpg&h=c315becc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國解放軍東部戰區官方微博公布第72集團軍某旅在駐地舉行的出征誓師動員大會影片。   圖：翻攝微博<br />\n<br />\n中國近期不斷對台文攻武嚇，頻頻派出戰機擾台，加劇台海緊張情勢。中國解放軍18日又釋出一段「出征誓師畫面」，鏡頭前1個不到1000人的兵力站在集合場，面向前方的高台聆訊，士兵們最後呼喊「全力打贏對手」，但詭異的是，影片一開始，官方就將片中指揮台的活動名稱打上馬賽克，僅透過貼文表示「在駐訓地舉行誓師動員大會」，遭中國網友痛批「見不得人？」<br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍東部戰區官方微博公布第72集團軍某旅在駐地舉行的出征誓師動員大會影片。45秒長的短片中可見，約有千名解放軍官兵列隊參與，他們宣讀誓詞，畫面兩邊則有多架坦克及裝甲車。不過，該影片片頭的場地兩側均有戰車，但片尾的場地旁則變成營帳；前方指揮台橫幅也被打上馬賽克，遮住活動名稱。種種被剪輯過的跡象，引發輿論關注。<br />\n<br />\n由於東部戰區第72集團軍向來被視為「攻台主力」，<span class=\"red\">中國網友紛紛興奮留言說：「我們一定要解放台灣」、「祖國統一大業拜託你們了」、「明天台北是不是能看見戰旗飄舞」。</span><br />\n<br />\n而中國《央視軍事》15日播出解放軍搶灘登陸演習畫面，被抓包將2015年的演習畫面剪入最新影片當中；<span class=\"red\">解放軍此次釋出影片馬上引發中國網友質疑：「為什麼要馬賽克？怕又被發現是舊視頻.....？」、「真好奇，趕快出去打，打勝了再說」、「又造假？見不得人嗎？」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/482/5f8cb6ddca801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F482%2F5f8cb6ddca801.jpg&h=21a9dfce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國官媒15日釋出的解放軍演習影片被抓包部分畫面來自2015年的演習場景。   圖：翻攝微博"},{"pid":"c8553c5808bdc52244f4e2fd7d7de77fbf0b41fa","tid":2249027,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/09/a3e066194f7224ee26097a5b2157ba2a-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fa3e066194f7224ee26097a5b2157ba2a-600x400.jpg&h=9264e7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共軍方日前發布的軍演畫面，與2016年12月央視公布的「2016火箭軍大演兵」的一樣。（視頻截圖）"},{"pid":"8b1e5787e908e70708ebff87df9d50c035ee20fb","tid":2249027,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wxlKif3S4nuaWu8CNG4Ddw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/77d94c0e8550626671445b641d1e15e1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwxlKif3S4nuaWu8CNG4Ddw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F77d94c0e8550626671445b641d1e15e1&h=1e31f56b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"793b64de038bc317e1eabeef6880b3bb6e9493ec","tid":2249027,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fj1wCjIitIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffj1wCjIitIU&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=9887c846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fj1wCjIitIU</a><br />\n解放軍空軍&ldquo;模擬轟-6K轟炸美軍基地&rdquo;視頻"},{"pid":"093fd6b383939308584413e8ba2473d36ccac1ed","tid":2249027,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/7483054836?is_all=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fu%2F7483054836%3Fis_all%3D1&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=100146c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://weibo.com/u/7483054836?is_all=1</a>"},{"pid":"5df6e655682a508f1f7a3a4a54375decde557436","tid":2249027,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm